  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b90\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba4 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "What is the request made by the Office of the Human Rights Commissioner?",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights has appealed to the authorities to exercise restraint in controlling the protestors in Sri Lanka today and has requested that all efforts be made to prevent violence.",
        "At the same time, we request the organizers of the demonstrations and their supporters to participate in the demonstrations in a peaceful manner and not to affect the essential medical and humanitarian services, said Raveena Samtasani, the spokesperson of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights.",
        "Human rights activists and journalists have the right to observe and report on demonstrations, so we appeal to the authorities to give a clear explanation to the soldiers that they should be protected while performing their duties and should not be prevented, he said."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "the Office of the Human Rights",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
